<subSubSection id="4E43B389EAB272FD0A1C14549E667041" pageId="null" pageNumber="145" type="description">
<paragraph id="E0E8206D1430FFE0E12A729E6C36A2A9" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">
Pflanze oft lockerrasig, mit langen kriechenden Stengeln. Untere 
<normalizedToken id="241FE57BC130E5C969DEB5629ECE6D66" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
oft ziemlich 
<normalizedToken id="05E25F9F635D562B0B875E1A31F70C04" originalValue="plötzlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">ploetzlich</normalizedToken>
in den Stiel 
<normalizedToken id="687F8146B831189F05C8BBBBB73C347A" originalValue="verschmälert" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">verschmaelert</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="690F3D5B596044CF68B1ADE4D3C020BB" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
hellila. 
<emphasis id="C639C28C6DAC73C255E2C5A09C91DCA3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">
<normalizedToken id="58AB8CFAA29B4092E8DECA04C78AFD60" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
2-6samig, mit 1-2 mm langem Griffel. Samen 1,6-2,4 mm lang.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="91EE36C76CC73CB71BC06D29902CB798" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="217FDA08C9BE10519CE84C3D00FEE1E7" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">
<emphasis id="335FC91863B55B32D15F2BB90B4DD18F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="367D5C5E04840F8C2F16BEF0786B2756" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">14:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischem Garten (Manton 1932), aus 
<normalizedToken id="BCA596EDBA9D6B80B122308948CA92FA" originalValue="Österreich" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">Oesterreich</normalizedToken>
(Mattick in Tischler 1950, Polatschek 1966).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D0E26DA4F0096AF867A30F99867F4BC1" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">
<emphasis id="14718E9FF895877D0C103B60EA1A7CFC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin und alpin. Ziemlich feuchter Kalkschutt. 
<emphasis id="0DC4A13849B1E00E11ECE5F9F1DF2D88" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">Thlaspeetum rotundifolii</emphasis>
Br.-Bl. 1926.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="582B18DFA3B86F04E341CC6734B939AC" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">
<emphasis id="CE14DF77F1A1C8A6D75A50DECB91CED4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">Verbreitung. Alpen-Pflanze:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="5B154E198948F8EDF9853A29A4D17912" originalValue="Nördliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">Noerdliche</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="DE162564C3D47B93E500799277373A5D" originalValue="südliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">suedliche</normalizedToken>
Kalkalpen. - Im Gebiet: Nordalpen und Bergamasker Alpen, Zentralalpen (
<normalizedToken id="675C78AE9AEDF587D2347EAFD24B53F4" originalValue="Mittelbünden" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">Mittelbuenden</normalizedToken>
, Umbrail?); zerstreut, ziemlich 
<normalizedToken id="294DC9C314BD4B3F70EC4EEC7C1F6272" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="145">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
